@startuml
!theme plain
title Project Coherent Storage - arXiv/RAG Metadata Workflow
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "Research topics" as Topics #D6EAF8
rectangle "arXiv export API\nsmall latest queries" as API #D5F5E3
rectangle "arXiv bulk data\nlarge metadata refresh" as Bulk #D5F5E3
rectangle "Rate-limit / failure log\nHTTP status + query string" as Fail #FADBD8
rectangle "RAG-DATA archive\nPDF / HTML / source tarball" as RAG #FCF3CF
rectangle "Evidence matrix\ndirect / adjacent / negative-control" as Matrix #E8DAEF
rectangle "Markdown reports" as MD #D7DBDD
rectangle "LaTeX + BibTeX\narXiv source package" as TEX #D7DBDD

Topics --> API
Topics --> Bulk
API --> RAG : metadata + PDF candidates
Bulk --> RAG : batch metadata
API --> Fail : 429 / timeout / parse error
Bulk --> Fail : access or schema issue
RAG --> Matrix
Matrix --> MD
Matrix --> TEX
Fail --> MD : disclose limitation
@enduml
